  "_note": "Per-entry _verification_status records sourcing. cross_references.* populated at X.D.1 back-fill (currently all null). The 13-37 00 00 umbrella entry is excluded from entries[] as the parent_category header. The secondary mirror exposes three level-3 sub-trees under 13-37: Performance Spaces (13-37 11), Display Spaces (13-37 13), and Creative Spaces (13-37 15). All 30 mirror-visible entries below the umbrella are included. Performance Spaces (13-37 11) sub-divides into Outdoor Theater (13-37 11 11), General Performance Spaces (13-37 11 13, 6 leaf entries), Audience Spaces (13-37 11 15, 2 leaf entries), and Supporting Performance Spaces (13-37 11 17, 4 leaf entries). Display Spaces (13-37 13) contains 5 leaf entries including Sculpture Garden and Ornamental Garden which receive ifc_space_type=EXTERNAL as outdoor open-air spaces per IfcSpaceTypeEnum (ISO 16739). Observation Deck (13-37 13 19) is also EXTERNAL. Creative Spaces (13-37 15) contains Recording Studio, Artist's Studio, Photo Lab (with one child), Media Production (with 2 children), and Zen Garden (EXTERNAL). All other entries are INTERNAL enclosed spaces. The entry_count_target of 16 is exceeded because the mirror coverage of 13-37 is dense across all three sub-trees. Future Sprint Y back-fill from the canonical OCCS PDF (CSI license) will raise _verification_status from mirror_sourced to occs_verified.",
